<!-- ============ THE VIVEN DIFFERENCE ============ -->
<section class="sec" id="difference">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-en="The Viven difference" data-de="Der Viven-Unterschied" data-es="La diferencia Viven">The Viven difference</span>
      <h2 data-en="Why brands choose us — and stay." data-de="Warum Marken uns wählen — und bleiben." data-es="Por qué las marcas nos eligen — y se quedan.">Why brands choose us — and stay.</h2>
      <p data-en="Four things we do differently. None of them optional." data-de="Vier Dinge, die wir anders machen. Keines davon ist optional." data-es="Cuatro cosas que hacemos distinto. Ninguna es opcional.">Four things we do differently. None of them optional.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 8h16v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H5a1 1 0 0 1-1-1z"/><path d="m4 8 2-5h3l-2 5"/><path d="m9 8 2-5h3l-2 5"/><path d="m14 8 2-5h3l-2 5"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-en="Feature-film discipline" data-de="Spielfilm-Disziplin" data-es="Disciplina de cine">Feature-film discipline</h3>
        <p data-en="The same rigor we bring to cinema, on every set: planned shots, tight schedules, zero wasted time." data-de="Dieselbe Präzision wie im Kino, an jedem Set: geplante Einstellungen, straffe Zeitpläne, keine verlorene Zeit." data-es="El mismo rigor del cine, en cada set: tomas planificadas, cronogramas ajustados, cero tiempo perdido.">The same rigor we bring to cinema, on every set: planned shots, tight schedules, zero wasted time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-en="Business-first thinking" data-de="Business-first-Denken" data-es="Mentalidad de negocio">Business-first thinking</h3>
        <p data-en="We start with your goal, not a camera. Every creative choice is tied to the outcome you need." data-de="Wir starten mit Ihrem Ziel, nicht mit einer Kamera. Jede kreative Entscheidung zahlt auf Ihr Ergebnis ein." data-es="Empezamos con tu objetivo, no con una cámara. Cada decisión creativa apunta al resultado que necesitas.">We start with your goal, not a camera. Every creative choice is tied to the outcome you need.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m12 2 8.5 5v10L12 22l-8.5-5V7z"/><path d="M12 22V12"/><path d="m3.5 7 8.5 5 8.5-5"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-en="Everything in-house" data-de="Alles aus einer Hand" data-es="Todo in-house">Everything in-house</h3>
